---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
import VisitorInfo from '../components/VisitorInfo.astro';

const { title = '首页 | 溯光', description = '探索、发现、热爱 — 技术笔记与生活手帐' } = Astro.props;
---

<Page {title} {description} hero>
  <div class="yun-home">
    <div class="yun-home-intro">
      <h2>最近更新</h2>
      <p>这里记录着代码与日常的缝隙之间，那些值得打捞的碎片。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="yun-card-grid">
      <article class="yun-card">
        <div class="yun-card-header">
          <h3 class="yun-card-title">在 TypeScript 中实现类型安全的 EventEmitter</h3>
          <div class="yun-card-meta">
            <span class="yun-card-date">2025-05-20</span>
            <span class="yun-card-category">技术</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="yun-card-content">
          <p>如何利用 TypeScript 4.1+ 的模板字面量类型和条件类型，构建一个完全类型安全的 EventEmitter。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="yun-card-actions">
          <a href="#" class="yun-card-action">阅读全文</a>
          <div class="yun-card-tags">
            <span class="yun-tag">TypeScript</span>
            <span class="yun-tag">事件系统</span>
            <span class="yun-tag">类型安全</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="yun-card">
        <div class="yun-card-header">
          <h3 class="yun-card-title">深夜咖啡馆与代码的对话</h3>
          <div class="yun-card-meta">
            <span class="yun-card-date">2025-05-18</span>
            <span class="yun-card-category">随笔</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="yun-card-content">
          <p>凌晨两点，咖啡馆的暖光打在键盘上。屏幕上的代码像一首未完成的诗。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="yun-card-actions">
          <a href="#" class="yun-card-action">阅读全文</a>
          <div class="yun-card-tags">
            <span class="yun-tag">生活</span>
            <span class="yun-tag">随笔</span>
            <span class="yun-tag">深夜</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="yun-card">
        <div class="yun-card-header">
          <h3 class="yun-card-title">Astro 3.0 新特性实战</h3>
          <div class="yun-card-meta">
            <span class="yun-card-date">2025-05-15</span>
            <span class="yun-card-category">前端</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="yun-card-content">
          <p>View Transitions API、Image 组件优化、Content Collections 增强……用实际项目体验 Astro 3.0 的开发效率提升。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="yun-card-actions">
          <a href="#" class="yun-card-action">阅读全文</a>
          <div class="yun-card-tags">
            <span class="yun-tag">Astro</span>
            <span class="yun-tag">前端</span>
            <span class="yun-tag">SSG</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="yun-card">
        <div class="yun-card-header">
          <h3 class="yun-card-title">黑曜石星光主题设计系统解析</h3>
          <div class="yun-card-meta">
            <span class="yun-card-date">2025-05-12</span>
            <span class="yun-card-category">设计</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="yun-card-content">
          <p>如何将黑曜石的深邃、星光的温暖、科技的冷感融合成一套完整的设计系统，并在实际项目中落地。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="yun-card-actions">
          <a href="#" class="yun-card-action">阅读全文</a>
          <div class="yun-card-tags">
            <span class="yun-tag">设计系统</span>
            <span class="yun-tag">UI/UX</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <aside class="yun-sidebar">
      <VisitorInfo />
      <div class="yun-widget">
        <h4>分类</h4>
        <ul class="yun-category-list">
          <li><a href="#">技术 (12)</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">随笔 (8)</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">前端 (15)</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">设计 (5)</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">生活 (10)</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="yun-widget">
        <h4>标签云</h4>
        <div class="yun-tag-cloud">
          <a href="#" class="yun-tag-cloud-item">TypeScript</a>
          <a href="#" class="yun-tag-cloud-item">Astro</a>
          <a href="#" class="yun-tag-cloud-item">设计系统</a>
          <a href="#" class="yun-tag-cloud-item">前端</a>
          <a href="#" class="yun-tag-cloud-item">生活</a>
          <a href="#" class="yun-tag-cloud-item">深夜</a>
          <a href="#" class="yun-tag-cloud-item">代码</a>
          <a href="#" class="yun-tag-cloud-item">随笔</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</Page>

<style>
  .yun-home {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 300px;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .yun-home-intro {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .yun-home-intro h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .yun-home-intro p {
    color: var(--va-c-text-light);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .yun-card-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .yun-card {
    background: var(--va-c-bg-light);
    border-radius: var(--yun-card-radius);
    padding: var(--yun-card-padding);
    border: 1px solid var(--va-c-divider);
    transition: all var(--duration-normal) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .yun-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    border-color: var(--va-c-primary);
  }

  .yun-card-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .yun-card-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    color: var(--va-c-text);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .yun-card-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--va-c-text-lighter);
  }

  .yun-card-date::before {
    content: '📅';
    margin-right: 4px;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .yun-card-category {
    background: var(--va-c-bg-soft);
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  .yun-card-content p {
    color: var(--va-c-text-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .yun-card-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--va-c-divider);
    padding-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .yun-card-action {
    color: var(--va-c-primary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .yun-card-action:hover {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--va-c-primary) 80%, black);
  }

  .yun-card-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .yun-tag {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 2px 10px;
    background: var(--va-c-bg-soft);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    color: var(--va-c-text-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--va-c-divider);
    transition: all var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .yun-tag:hover {
    background: var(--va-c-primary);
    color: white;
    border-color: var(--va-c-primary);
  }

  .yun-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: calc(var(--yun-nav-height) + var(--space-lg));
  }

  .yun-widget {
    background: var(--va-c-bg-light);
    border-radius: var(--yun-card-radius);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--va-c-divider);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .yun-widget h4 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--va-c-text);
  }

  .yun-category-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .yun-category-list li {
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .yun-category-list a {
    display: block;
    padding: 6px 0;
    color: var(--va-c-text-light);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--va-c-divider);
    transition: all var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .yun-category-list a:hover {
    color: var(--va-c-primary);
    border-color: var(--va-c-primary);
  }

  .yun-tag-cloud {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .yun-tag-cloud-item {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    background: var(--va-c-bg-soft);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    color: var(--va-c-text-light);
    border: 1px solid var(--va-c-divider);
    transition: all var(--duration-fast) var(--ease-out);
  }

  .yun-tag-cloud-item:hover {
    background: var(--va-c-primary);
    color: white;
    border-color: var(--va-c-primary);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .yun-home {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .yun-sidebar {
      position: static;
      margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .yun-card {
      padding: var(--space-md);
    }
    .yun-card-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: var(--space-sm);
    }
  }
</style>